Title: Mung-Mung's Vote I: A Hozen's Problem
Description:
I've been thinkin' about how to get into the Tiller's good graces, $n.

Now, the Tiller's Union accepts new farmers each year, and there are five members on the voting council.

We already got Gina's vote, but we'll have to prove ourselves to the other four members of their board.

Why don't you go over and say hello to Mung-Mung? He works with Mr. Mudclaw out on the Mudclaw's farm to the northwest.
ObjectivesText: Speak to Mung-Mung at Haohan Mudclaw's House in the Valley of the Four Winds.
